A basic calculator program written in Python that allows users to perform simple arithmetic operations 
such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.


✨ Features

Perform basic arithmetic operations:

➕ Addition

➖ Subtraction

✖️ Multiplication

➗ Division

User-friendly input and output
Handles continuous calculations


🖼️ Example

Enter first number: 10  
Enter operator (+, -, *, /):  
Result: 50


🛠️ Technologies

Python 3

